# Portfolio Tracker Cursor Rules

## Scope
- Apply to all files in this repository.

## Tech Stack
- Electron + React + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS.
- Local database uses Dexie (IndexedDB).
- State management uses Zustand.

## Coding Style
- Keep changes minimal and focused.
- Prefer shared utilities over duplicated matching logic.
- Use explicit TypeScript types for interfaces and public helpers.
- Keep UI text in Simplified Chinese unless a technical term is English.

## Data Rules
- Multi-user data must be isolated by `influencerId`.
- Default influencer is `八喜`.
- Do not introduce cross-user leakage in snapshots/holdings/analysis reads.

## UI Rules
- Follow industrial light theme defined in `src/renderer/src/index.css`.
- Keep industry color mapping centralized in `src/renderer/src/utils/industry.ts`.
- Feature flags / provider switches should remain env-driven.

## Quality Gates
- Before commit: run `npm run typecheck`.
- Prefer fixing lint warnings in touched files.

